---
title: Double Golden Coconut Fish & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice
description: There’s something about a fish curry - all those bold flavours with delicate, flaky fish? Yes please! This one has a rich coconut-infused sauce, punchy katsu paste and crisp veggies. Serve it generously over fluffy rice for the ultimate comfort meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/679c67dc3239984d76151a3e-8f3d4663.jpeg
